# Frontend architecture (scoped)

When editing UI files:

1. Load skill `frontend-architecture` for new features or structural changes
2. Keep components thin — data fetching in RSC/server layer or dedicated hooks
3. Use design tokens / shared primitives — run `impeccable` for polish audits
4. Animation: prefer `gsap-*` skills for scroll/timelines; see tech catalog for Framer Motion
5. Every interactive surface needs loading, error, and empty states where applicable

Stack-specific skills: [docs/TECH_STACK_SKILLS.md](../../docs/TECH_STACK_SKILLS.md)
